    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Yeah, that part is already working, but the issue is that we want to store the state in the url, like the other widgets already do. So there should be a extra query parameter in the url, for example paginator=5.\n\nWhen the visitor refreshes the page or when he visited a productpage and uses the back button in the browser we need to show the number of results that the visitor was looking at, for example 50 products.\n",
    "created_at": "2016-07-05T14:56:09Z",
